results.name: Coefficients in expansion of Dirichlet series Product_p (1 - (Kronecker(m,p) + 1)*p^(-s) + Kronecker(m,p)*p^(-2s))^(-1) for m = 25.
comment: Number of divisors of n not congruent to 0 mod 5.
link: Amiram Eldar, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
formula: Multiplicative with a(5^e)=1 and a(p^e)=e+1 for p<>5.
Moebius transform is period 5 sequence [ 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, ...]. - _Michael Somos_, Oct 31 2006
G.f.: Sum_{k>=1} x^k*(1 + x^k + x^(2*k) + x^(3*k))/(1 - x^(5*k)). - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Sep 11 2019
maple: for n from 1 to 500 do a := ifactors(n):s := 1:for k from 1 to nops(a[2]) do p := a[2][k][1]:e := a[2][k][2]: if p=5 then b := 1:else b := e+1:fi:s := s*b:od:printf(`%d,`,s); od:
mathematica: f[5, e_] := 1; f[p_, e_] := e+1; a[1] = 1; a[n_] := Times @@ f @@@ FactorInteger[n]; Array[a, 100] (* _Amiram Eldar_, Sep 26 2020 *)
xref: Cf. A116073 (sum of divisors of n not congruent to 0 mod 5).
